biography: Tommy, a golfer known for his calculated approach and unwavering focus, hails from Espoo Ringside Golf. Despite his calm demeanor on the course, those who know Tommy well can attest to his fiery competitive spirit.

Tommy is gearing up to make his third appearance at the Hector Trophée in 2025. While the coveted Hector Trophée and the Victor Trophy have eluded him thus far, Tommy's dedication and strategic prowess make him a formidable contender in every tournament he enters. His fans eagerly anticipate seeing his continued growth and performance in the upcoming years.
